max flow / min cut today

flow = respect capacities + conservation at internal nodes  
cut = partition with s in S, t in T, capacity = sum edges S→T

ford-fulkerson: start zero, push on augmenting paths in residual until stuck

$|f|$ = net out of source (same as net into sink)

